  <brief_title>Treatment of the Infections on Osteo-articular Prostheses by 6 Versus 12 Weeks of Antibiotherapy</brief_title>
  <acronym>DATIPO</acronym>
  <official_title>Multicentric Study, of Non Inferiority, Randomized, Opened, to Evaluate the Two Durations Effectiveness of Antibiotherapy (6 Weeks Versus 12 Weeks) in the Treatment of Osteo-articular Prostheses Infections, With Prosthetic Change (in 1 Time or 2 Long Times) or Not (Articular Washing)</official_title>
